629", "card_id": "Q_621617850", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "被困缅甸的中科院博士发声，称已于 9 月 5 日返回国内，后续会对一些问题进行解释，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "被困缅甸的中科院博士发声：已于 9 月 5 日回国。 据封面新闻，9 月 11 日，此前因「中科院博士被骗至缅甸事件」引发关注的当事人发文：我已于 9 月 5 日返回国内，因配合调查和个人生病不适的原因，一直未能发文。本着对公众和自己负责的态度，后续我会对大家关注的一些问题进行解释。 从事件发酵到顺利返回，我克服了重重阻碍，这既离不开亲人和朋友的奉献，也离不开政府部门、新闻媒体、社会热心人士的关注和支持，因精力有限我无法一一答谢，但愿未来能尽我所能回报社会，避免更多人遭受同样的苦难。 被困缅甸的中科院博士发声：已于 9 月 5 日回国。-24 小时 - 虎嗅网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d6044458d95f2f75d8638daa72d60579_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "153 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/621617850"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ikpz9hf/A8/BwEAMaCTEwMDQxNjk4NiD05/6nBjAAOHRACHIJNjIxNjE3ODUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1694532171.445506", "card_id": "Q_380813424", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "使用电报 App 时间久了后会有什么错觉?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我先来，一段 10 秒的视频才 800KB，画质也还行。 我突然觉得自个下载几十 GB 的蓝光电影来看实在是有病"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "122 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/380813424"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ikpz9hf/A8/BwEAMaCDQ2OTAzNTM4IMKIzfMFMAA4hAFACXIJMzgwODEzNDI0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"t